29.21	Smiles_of_a_Summer_Night	Smiles of a Summer Night	Smiles of a Summer Night a.k.a. Smiles on a Summer Night (Swedish: ) is a 1955 Swedish comedy film directed by Ingmar Bergman. It was the first of Bergman's films to bring the director international success, due to its exposure at the 1956 Cannes Film Festival. In 2005 it was on TIME magazine's "100 Movies" list of the best movies of all time.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/c9/Smilessummernight.jpg/220px-Smilessummernight.jpg
